-------------------------------
- Install the Nutanix Operator

-- Move to the good folder
cd /nutanix/operator

-- Update the operator channel and catalog
vim overlay/airgapped-lab/kustomization.yaml
  - Update the channel and source "value"

-- Install the Nutanix operator
oc create -k overlay/airgapped-lab/

- Monitor Nutanix Operator installation
oc get all -n openshift-cluster-csi-drivers

-------------------------------
- Install the Nutanix instance

-- Move to the good folder
cd /nutanix/instance

-- Install


- Monitor Nutanix Operator installation
oc get all -n openshift-cluster-csi-drivers
